1
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:08,060
This is great.

2
00:00:08,140 --> 00:00:10,699
Public opinion has
shifted from your resignation

3
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,740
to the technical difficulties of
Qingniao and Minghui Groups.

4
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:17,779
It's triggering deep
reflection across the industry

5
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:20,260
on basic computing power and
core technological independence.

6
00:00:20,620 --> 00:00:22,540
That's exactly what
we wanted to express.

7
00:00:23,100 --> 00:00:24,820
Now we just have to see if it works

8
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,660
and if everyone agrees to
the mobilization of computing resources.

9
00:00:32,300 --> 00:00:33,540
Shen Gu.

10
00:00:39,100 --> 00:00:40,099
Hello?

11
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:41,339
Well done,

12
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:42,620
Producer Song.

13
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:44,340
You too.

14
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:47,220
I'm sorry.

15
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:50,460
I have still made you worry
about the company matters.

16
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,540
You should be proud of me.

17
00:00:55,940 --> 00:00:57,220
I am very proud.

18
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:01,140
You must not have
rested well last night.

19
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:02,820
It's my fault.

20
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,699
Then, Mr. Shen,

21
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:08,140
why don't you write
a long apology to reflect on it?

22
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:11,340
Fine.

23
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:14,500
I'll keep reflecting
until you're satisfied.

24
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:22,540
Let's talk later.

25
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:26,939
Hello.

26
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,060
Miss Xu.

27
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:29,540
Hello.

28
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:31,939
Your speech just now
was brilliant, Miss Xu.

29
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:34,419
If Raymond Technology can team up
with other tech companies today

30
00:01:34,420 --> 00:01:35,899
to pressure Yinghai Group,

31
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:37,899
they will use the same
tactics to suppress us tomorrow.

32
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,139
What we need now

33
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:40,739
is a stronger resistance against them.

34
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:41,299
Miss Xu,

35
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:43,300
you really taught us a lesson today.

36
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,500
We all understand that if one falls,
the rest will follow.

37
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:49,900
Mr. Fang, I'm sorry
about what happened last time.

38
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,499
We have considered it thoroughly.

39
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:53,220
We can sign the contract right now.

40
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:57,539
That's right. As long as we join forces,

41
00:01:57,540 --> 00:01:59,899
I don't believe Yinghai Group will
give up the entire East Asian market

42
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,899
just for Raymond Group.

43
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:03,619
Thank you for your trust.

44
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:05,099
Let's show them

45
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:07,019
the meaning of absolute unity.

46
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:08,140
Good.

47
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:12,020
Let's officially launch
the Emergency Mutual Aid Agreement.

48
00:02:12,140 --> 00:02:14,179
Thank you for joining voluntarily.

49
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,819
Let's complete the first batch of
computing power transfers before dawn

50
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:18,579
to support the Spark system.

51
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:20,340
- Alright!
- Alright!

52
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:21,899
=Echoes of Gang City=
Alright.

53
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,080
That's wonderful.

54
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:29,520
=Episode 24=
(By Your Side in This Life)

55
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:38,940
Having you all by Wanxin's side

56
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,619
is her good fortune.

57
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,779
Wanxin has been at
our TV station for eight years.

58
00:02:42,780 --> 00:02:44,740
I care for her like my own daughter.

59
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:46,620
Wanxin, let's get down to business.

60
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:50,779
Qingniao Group's technical staff
is stranded at the airport.

61
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:52,499
Mr. Fang has
already gone to resolve that.

62
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,019
But what we need now is

63
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:57,699
to coordinate and mobilize resources,
equipment, and talent from peers

64
00:02:57,700 --> 00:02:59,140
to handle the emergency for Qingniao.

65
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:02,060
We need a large amount of capital.

66
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:05,019
Wanxin, you don't need
to worry about that.

67
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,819
I've already spoken with my mother.

68
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:09,419
She will provide
enough funds to support us.

69
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:10,540
Mr. Fang,

70
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:13,020
we can't let your
family bear all the risks.

71
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:16,420
I've discussed it with Grandfather.

72
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:20,500
We've decided to use
group equity as collateral

73
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:23,220
to complete the formal
loan approval process.

74
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,779
Wanxin, no need for collateral.

75
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:28,579
The Song Group will also
mobilize all available funds

76
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:29,820
to help you.

77
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:32,060
Qionghua,

78
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:36,099
Wanxin's intention is also mine.

79
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,899
We invited you here today

80
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:41,460
to convey these decisions to you.

81
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:43,740
Count me in.

82
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,420
Dad,

83
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:51,299
I know my elder brother
is better than me

84
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,500
and smarter than me.

85
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,140
But after all, I'm also your son.

86
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,020
It has already come to this point.

87
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:59,500
I can still tell who is on our side.

88
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:01,300
If we need equity collateral,
then so be it.

89
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,420
If it's not enough,

90
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,820
you can include my shares as well.

91
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:08,860
Uncle Zhaohui,

92
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:11,060
thank you.

93
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,820
No need to thank me.

94
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:14,420
This is what I should do.

95
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:17,260
Come, you should sit down too.

96
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:27,379
I invited you here today

97
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:29,179
because there is one more thing to say.

98
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:31,860
I want to introduce someone to you.

99
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:59,220
Boss,

100
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:01,899
the first batch of resources
from Miss Xu and Lawyer Fang

101
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,499
has departed from Gang City

102
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:05,020
and will arrive at headquarters soon.

103
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,779
From the current state
of the computing system,

104
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:09,219
it's enough to support the continuous
operation of the Spark system.

105
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,299
But

106
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:12,860
we currently don't have
a suitable technical team.

107
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,540
Expand the search area.

108
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:18,779
With these allocated
resources as support,

109
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:20,699
it has already bought us a lot of time.

110
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:21,579
Raymond Group and Junlin Group

111
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:24,139
are competing with us for talent
using equity incentive plans.

112
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,579
Raymond Group is
an established tech company.

113
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:27,300
Judging from the current situation,

114
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:28,899
whether it's in terms of employment

115
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,260
or future scientific research results,

116
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:32,820
we are at a disadvantage.

117
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:39,020
Shen Gu.

118
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:03,980
Dr. Sun.

119
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:06,460
This is my husband, Shen Gu.

120
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:09,379
Hello, Dr. Sun.

121
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:10,419
I've heard so much about you.

122
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,740
Hello, Shen Gu.

123
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:15,099
Wanxin told me
everything about your situation.

124
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,660
We are willing to join forces with you

125
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:20,460
to carry out technical development
alongside Minghui's results.

126
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,940
Thank you so much.

127
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,420
Thank you, everyone.

128
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:25,900
Li Yan.

129
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:27,540
Dr. Sun, please come inside.

130
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:49,790
Wanxin,

131
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:51,420
thank you.

132
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:59,170
♪The clouds hide the faint light
behind them♪

133
00:07:00,140 --> 00:07:04,270
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

134
00:07:04,610 --> 00:07:08,620
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

135
