178
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:21,100
Mr. Tingyuan,

179
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:23,060
what are you worried about?

180
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:29,180
There has been no news at all
from Shen Gu and his team.

181
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:30,900
I'm just afraid...

182
00:10:32,140 --> 00:10:33,460
Don't worry.

183
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:37,820
Right now, all the technical
personnel in the world are in our hands.

184
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:41,220
Do you know how much
manpower and resources

185
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:44,140
