the technological barrier?

186
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:48,060
Shen Gu and his team won't be able
to break through it in a short time.

187
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:50,420
Besides,

188
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:52,900
we are using
the lawsuit to stall for time.

189
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:55,820
Yinghai has an excuse to
keep cutting off Qingniao's supply.

190
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:59,220
We'll wear them down sooner or later.

191
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,420
Good.

192
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,939
Hello everyone.
This is the news scene outside

193
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:12,819
the headquarters of
Qingniao Group in Shen City.

194
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:14,099
The facade of the building behind me

195
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:17,339
is covered with giant dynamic posters
of the Spark supercomputing system.

196
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:19,939
After experiencing
a unilateral supply suspension,

197
00:11:19,940 --> 00:11:23,099
Qingniao Group today
officially announced to the world

198
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:25,819
its self-developed
supercomputing solution,

199
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:27,779
marking a breakthrough
in key technologies

200
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:29,820
within the field of
high-performance computing.

201
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:30,579
The Spark system

202
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:33,420
uses Qingniao's original
quantum-state encryption technology

203
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,740
and deeply integrates Minghui's patents.

204
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:38,939
The tested computing density can reach
80 percent of Yinghai's capacity.

205
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:40,139
In other words,

206
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:42,019
we have successfully broken
through a major technical barrier

207
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:44,140
in the field of AI computing power.

208
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:48,699
The cooperation is by no means limited
to Minghui's technology licensing.

209
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:51,060
(Spark, Minghui Group, Qingniao Group)
Relying on Qingniao's Spark system,

210
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:52,699
Minghui Group's biotechnology team

211
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,379
has made a breakthrough.

212
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:58,220
AI pathological identification achieves
digital quantification in 30 seconds.

213
00:11:58,300 --> 00:12:00,379
Promoting the development
of digital pathology

214
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:02,739
has become a perfect practical case

215
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:04,620
for Qingniao Group in other fields.

216
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,019
Qingniao and Minghui

217
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:10,620
have built a deeply
integrated strategic community.

218
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:13,699
Both parties have formed
a technical closed loop in areas

219
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:15,540
such as computing
infrastructure and bio-intelligence,

220
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,979
jointly promoting
future intelligent upgrades.

221
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,100
Finally,

222
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:22,219
I would like to thank you,
Ms. Xu Wanxin,

223
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:24,020
for the support you
provided to Qingniao.

224
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,820
Today's research results from Qingniao

225
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:28,620
would not have been
possible without your help.

226
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:38,680
(Spark, Minghui Group, Qingniao Group)

227
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:17,740
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

228
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:24,820
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

229
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:30,900
♪You turn and look back at me♪

230
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:37,540
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

231
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:44,020
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

232
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:50,780
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

233
00:13:51,900 --> 00:13:57,220
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

234
00:13:58,380 --> 00:14:04,180
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

235
00:14:04,580 --> 00:14:11,540
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

236
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:17,340
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

237
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:24,379
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

238
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:27,259
♪The promise we made♪

239
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:30,939
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

240
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:37,539
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

241
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:43,940
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

242
00:14:44,340 --> 00:14:50,659
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

243
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:55,780
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

244
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:59,260
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
